        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:08.100",
        "end": "00:09.900",
        "original": "かけるよ",
        "english": "I'll cast",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:09.900",
        "end": "00:12.800",
        "original": "We can stay oh yeah!",
        "english": "We can stay oh yeah!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:31.900",
        "end": "00:35.300",
        "original": "最高のステージだったよ、ホロウィッチ。",
        "english": "That was an amazing stage, holoWitches.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:35.600",
        "end": "00:37.400",
        "original": "ほんと、ほんと！",
        "english": "Totally, totally!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:37.400",
        "end": "00:39.600",
        "original": "みんな、お疲れ様。",
        "english": "Good job, everyone.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:39.900",
        "end": "00:41.300",
        "original": "カノンさん、",
        "english": "Kanon-san,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:41.300",
        "end": "00:46.400",
        "original": "あの、今日は本当にありがとうございました。",
        "english": "um, thank you so much for today.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:47.300",
        "end": "00:52.200",
        "original": "それで、あなたはどうして、夢落ちとか僕たちのことを？",
        "english": "So, why do you know about Dreamfalls and us?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:53.300",
        "end": "00:55.700",
        "original": "私、前に夢落ちして",
        "english": "I fell into a Dreamfall before...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:55.700",
        "end": "00:59.000",
        "original": "君たちに助けられたことがあるんだ。",
        "english": "...and you girls saved me.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:00.800",
        "end": "01:02.100",
        "original": "ええーっ！？",
        "english": "What!?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:02.200",
        "end": "01:05.500",
        "original": "だから、あの時の自分と同じように",
        "english": "So, just like I was back then...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:05.500",
        "end": "01:11.800",
        "original": "夢落ちして苦しんでいる誰かを見ると、放っておけなくて。",
        "english": "...I can't just leave someone behind when I see them suffering from a Dreamfall.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:12.600",
        "end": "01:14.600",
        "original": "あと、実は...",
        "english": "Also, actually...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:15.500",
        "end": "01:19.400",
        "original": "今日このステージに出ることにしたのも",
        "english": "The reason I decided to appear on this stage today...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:19.400",
        "end": "01:23.000",
        "original": "君たちが出ると聞いたからなんだ。",
        "english": "...was because I heard you girls were going to be here.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:23.000",
        "end": "01:25.700",
        "original": "もう一度会えたらって思って。",
        "english": "I thought I might be able to see you again.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:26.500",
        "end": "01:29.800",
        "original": "だから今日は、えっと...",
        "english": "So today, um...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:30.200",
        "end": "01:32.400",
        "original": "すごく嬉しかった！",
        "english": "...I was very happy!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:33.200",
        "end": "01:35.800",
        "original": "これからも頑張ってね、ホロウィッチ。",
        "english": "Keep doing your best, holoWitches.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:36.400",
        "end": "01:37.800",
        "original": "そ、それじゃあ。",
        "english": "W-well then.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:41.000",
        "end": "01:44.200",
        "original": "また！ぜひまた！",
        "english": "See ya! For sure, see ya again!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:50.800",
        "end": "01:55.300",
        "original": "あの人自身が夢落ちしてホロウィッチに助けられていたから",
        "english": "Because he was saved by holoWitches when he fell into a Dreamfall himself...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:56.400",
        "end": "01:59.200",
        "original": "知っていたんだ。夢落ちした時の辛さも",
        "english": "...he knew. He knew the pain of falling into a Dreamfall...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:59.200",
        "end": "02:05.600",
        "original": "そんな時、誰かが手を差し伸べてくれることの嬉しさも。",
        "english": "...and the joy of someone reaching out their hand in a time like that.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:06.500",
        "end": "02:11.700",
        "original": "そっか。みこたちが少しでも誰かの力になれたら",
        "english": "I see. If we can be even a little bit of a source of strength for someone...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:12.300",
        "end": "02:17.100",
        "original": "その誰かが、また別の誰かの力になってくれるんだね。",
        "english": "...then that someone will, in turn, become a source of strength for someone else.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:17.400",
        "end": "02:20.100",
        "original": "そうだね。しかもさ、そんだけじゃなくて",
        "english": "Right. And it's not just that...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:20.100",
        "end": "02:23.500",
        "original": "うちらの力になってくれたりもするわけじゃん。",
        "english": "...they also become a source of strength for us, don't they?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:23.900",
        "end": "02:27.700",
        "original": "あの人や、今日応援してくれたみんなみたいに。",
        "english": "Like him, and everyone who supported us today.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:28.100",
        "end": "02:29.600",
        "original": "それって...",
        "english": "That's...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:29.900",
        "end": "02:31.400",
        "original": "それって...",
        "english": "That's...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:31.700",
        "end": "02:34.500",
        "original": "それってすっごく...",
        "english": "That's super...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:34.700",
        "end": "02:38.000",
        "original": "すっごくトリート！",
        "english": "...Super Treat!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:08.500",
        "end": "03:12.700",
        "original": "キラキラ 宝石みたいに輝いてる",
        "english": "Sparkling, shining like a gem",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:13.200",
        "end": "03:19.400",
        "original": "夢の結晶 みんなの宝物",
        "english": "Crystals of dreams, everyone's treasure",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:19.500",
        "end": "03:23.900",
        "original": "時々 見失っちゃうこともあるけど",
        "english": "Sometimes we might lose sight of it, but...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:24.300",
        "end": "03:29.500",
        "original": "あふれ出した 光が僕を呼ぶんだよ",
        "english": "...the overflowing light calls out to me",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:31.300",
        "end": "03:34.400",
        "original": "絶対 大丈夫",
        "english": "You'll definitely be okay",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:34.400",
        "end": "03:41.200",
        "original": "ただ まっすぐでいることも 楽じゃない日もあるよね",
        "english": "There are days when even just staying true to yourself isn't easy",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:42.500",
        "end": "03:45.000",
        "original": "諦めも",
        "english": "Giving up...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:45.300",
        "end": "03:48.000",
        "original": "苦しみも",
        "english": "...and suffering...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:48.000",
        "end": "03:52.400",
        "original": "重ねていこう 心叩き 放とう",
        "english": "...let's let them pile up, and then let our hearts beat and release them",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:53.600",
        "end": "03:56.500",
        "original": "夢を 歌おう",
        "english": "Let's sing our dreams",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:56.500",
        "end": "03:59.300",
        "original": "魔法に乗せて",
        "english": "Riding on magic",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:59.500",
        "end": "04:04.200",
        "original": "何度も 立ち上がる 君と一緒に進んでく",
        "english": "Standing up again and again, I'll keep moving forward with you",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:04.300",
